name: Ahegao, rolling eyes(realistic)
description:
Ahegao in common sd models tend to be Anime style (and lacks of expression like rolling eyes), so I trained this lora on 20 photos as title. (Nice website to recommend. Plz! Keep in low profile.)

Suggested weighted 0.5~0.95(it depends on your model & feel free to try). This can go with my merged checkpoint.
